data.text:
5.00% Annual Percentage Yield Preferred Savings

Morgan Stanley clients with eligible brokerage accounts can earn 5.00% APY through deposits into our Preferred Savings Program for qualifying cash. Contact our team to learn more or click here for more details. Terms apply.

Explore our Enhanced Spending + Budgeting Tool

We’ve enhanced our Spending + Budgeting experience with advanced tools to help you organize transactions and customize your financial view. Learn more.

The Age of AI and Other Trends in Tech and Beyond

AI beyond the hype, a potential breakthrough in health tech, a near-term opportunity in PCs and more trends in technology and beyond.

Help Improve Your After-Tax Returns with Tax Management Services

Help keep more of your returns and potentially reduce tax liability with a tax-managed investment portfolio. Learn more.

Cybersecurity Resources

At Morgan Stanley, safeguarding your assets and personal information is among our highest priorities. Learn about our security measures and use our resources and ideas to help protect yourself online.

A $695 Annual Engagement Bonus

For eligible Platinum CashPlus Brokerage Account clients with The Platinum Card® from American Express Exclusively for Morgan Stanley. Certain Morgan Stanley Debit Card holders may also qualify. Terms apply.

Cash Back is Simply Rewarding

The Morgan Stanley Blue Cash Preferred® American Express Card. Earn cash back on U.S. supermarkets, U.S. gas and more. Eligibility & terms apply. Learn More.

LET’S TALK ABOUT YOU

As we work together to map out a plan that helps achieve your financial goals, our goal is to learn what is important to you. Discover how our goals-based planning process takes into account all of your financial needs to deliver a customized plan.
